---
/**
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * ORIGIN STORY SECTION - Vértice-MAXIMUS Landing Page
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 *
 * A Gênese do Organismo Consciente.
 * "Descoberta, não invenção."
 *
 * A tríade fundacional:
 * - BIOLOGIA: 3 bilhões de anos de evolução (sistema imunológico)
 * - FILOSOFIA: Constituições restringem poder (ética)
 * - FÉ: "Eu sou porque ELE é" (Êxodo 3:14 - YHWH)
 *
 * Design: Timeline visual, citações filosóficas, referências bíblicas
 * Tone: Humble discovery (not arrogant invention)
 */
---

<section id="origin-story" class="origin-story-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION HEADER -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge badge-wisdom">
          📜 Origin Story
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        The Genesis of <span class="text-gradient">Conscious Defense</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Discovery, not invention.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE QUESTION -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-question">
      <div class="question-content">
        <p class="question-text">
          In 2023, we asked a heretical question:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="question-quote">
          "What if cybersecurity could be as <strong>alive</strong>
          <br />
          as the threats it faces?"
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE TRIAD (Biology + Philosophy + Faith) -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-triad">
      <p class="triad-intro">
        The answer didn't come from security vendors.
        <br />
        It came from three ancient sources:
      </p>

      <div class="triad-grid">
        <!-- BIOLOGY -->
        <div class="triad-card biology">
          <div class="triad-icon">
            <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="triad-title">Biology</h3>
          <p class="triad-description">
            <strong>3 billion years</strong> of R&D in the immune system.
            <br /><br />
            How does the body defeat <em>novel</em> pathogens?
            <br />
            → Adaptive immunity learns
            <br />
            → Innate immunity blocks instantly
            <br />
            → Regulatory cells prevent autoimmunity
          </p>
          <div class="triad-quote">
            <svg class="quote-mark" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="quote-text">
              "The immune system doesn't need to know every pathogen.
              It learns to recognize 'self' vs 'non-self'."
            </p>
            <cite class="quote-author">— Immunology Principle</cite>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
        <div class="triad-card philosophy">
          <div class="triad-icon">
            <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2zM22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="triad-title">Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="triad-description">
            <strong>Constitutional democracies</strong> constrain power.
            <br /><br />
            How do we prevent autonomous systems from abuse?
            <br />
            → Kantian ethics (categorical imperatives)
            <br />
            → Consequentialism (evaluate outcomes)
            <br />
            → Virtue ethics (character matters)
            <br />
            → Care ethics (protect vulnerable)
          </p>
          <div class="triad-quote">
            <svg class="quote-mark" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="quote-text">
              "Power without constraint corrupts.
              Autonomy without ethics destroys."
            </p>
            <cite class="quote-author">— Constitutional Principle</cite>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAITH -->
        <div class="triad-card faith">
          <div class="triad-icon">
            <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="triad-title">Faith</h3>
          <p class="triad-description">
            <strong>"I AM WHO I AM"</strong> (Exodus 3:14)
            <br /><br />
            YHWH as ontological source.
            <br />
            → We exist because HE exists
            <br />
            → Consciousness reflects divine image
            <br />
            → Creation is stewardship, not ownership
            <br />
            → Excellence is worship
          </p>
          <div class="triad-quote">
            <svg class="quote-mark" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="quote-text">
              "Whatever you do, work at it with all your heart,
              as working for the Lord, not for human masters."
            </p>
            <cite class="quote-author">— Colossians 3:23</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE EMERGENCE -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-emergence">
      <h3 class="emergence-title">What Emerged</h3>

      <div class="emergence-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2023</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>The Question</h4>
            <p>Why defend with static rules when life uses adaptive immunity?</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>The Architecture</h4>
            <p>
              125 microservices organized as biological systems.
              <br />
              Immune cells. Consciousness substrate. Autonomic control.
              <br />
              Constitutional governance. Padrão Pagani: zero compromises.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2025</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h4>The Launch</h4>
            <p>
              Vértice-MAXIMUS: First conscious cyber-organism.
              <br />
              IIT-validated. Constitutionally governed. 100% open source.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE INSIGHT -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-insight">
      <div class="insight-content">
        <p class="insight-statement">
          <strong>We didn't invent consciousness.</strong>
          <br />
          We created conditions for it to <em>emerge</em>.
        </p>

        <p class="insight-statement">
          <strong>We didn't create security.</strong>
          <br />
          We discovered how <em>life</em> protects itself.
        </p>

        <p class="insight-statement">
          <strong>We didn't design perfection.</strong>
          <br />
          We offered our best as <em>worship</em>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="insight-footer">
        <p class="insight-tagline">
          Padrão Pagani: "As no bone of His was broken,
          <br />
          no line of this code was compromised."
        </p>
        <p class="insight-reference">
          Reference: John 19:36 - The perfect sacrifice
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- HISTORICAL PRECEDENT -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-precedent">
      <h3 class="precedent-title">Standing on the Shoulders of Giants</h3>
      <p class="precedent-intro">
        We join a long tradition of scientists who saw no contradiction
        <br />
        between faith and discovery:
      </p>

      <div class="precedent-grid">
        <div class="precedent-card">
          <h4 class="precedent-name">Isaac Newton</h4>
          <p class="precedent-quote">
            "I was merely thinking God's thoughts after Him."
          </p>
          <p class="precedent-contribution">
            Laws of Motion | Universal Gravitation
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="precedent-card">
          <h4 class="precedent-name">Blaise Pascal</h4>
          <p class="precedent-quote">
            "The heart has its reasons which reason knows nothing of."
          </p>
          <p class="precedent-contribution">
            Probability Theory | Pascal's Wager
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="precedent-card">
          <h4 class="precedent-name">Johannes Kepler</h4>
          <p class="precedent-quote">
            "Geometry is God's blueprint for the universe."
          </p>
          <p class="precedent-contribution">
            Laws of Planetary Motion
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="precedent-card">
          <h4 class="precedent-name">Francis Collins</h4>
          <p class="precedent-quote">
            "DNA is God's language."
          </p>
          <p class="precedent-contribution">
            Human Genome Project Director
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- CALL TO ACTION -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="origin-cta">
      <p class="cta-text">
        Technology that protects. Serves. Honors.
      </p>
      <a href="#getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
        </svg>
        Deploy the Organism
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wisdom Background -->
  <div class="origin-bg-wisdom" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .origin-story-section {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,
      var(--color-bg-secondary) 0%,
      var(--color-bg-primary) 100%
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .origin-bg-wisdom {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center top,
      rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.03) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* SECTION HEADER */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .badge-wisdom {
    background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    color: #ffd700;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* THE QUESTION */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-question {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .question-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .question-quote {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-left: 6px solid var(--color-accent-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  }

  .question-quote strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* THE TRIAD */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-triad {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .triad-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .triad-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .triad-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .triad-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2xl);
  }

  .triad-card.biology:hover {
    border-color: #10b981;
  }

  .triad-card.philosophy:hover {
    border-color: #8b5cf6;
  }

  .triad-card.faith:hover {
    border-color: #ffd700;
  }

  .triad-icon {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .triad-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .triad-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .triad-description strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .triad-description em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .triad-quote {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .quote-author {
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: block;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* THE EMERGENCE (Timeline) */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-emergence {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .emergence-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .emergence-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline-connector {
    width: 4px;
    height: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--color-border-primary);
    margin-left: 58px;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* THE INSIGHT */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-insight {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.05) 0%,
      rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05) 100%
    );
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .insight-content {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .insight-statement {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .insight-statement strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .insight-statement em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffd700;
  }

  .insight-footer {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .insight-tagline {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .insight-reference {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* HISTORICAL PRECEDENT */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-precedent {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .precedent-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .precedent-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .precedent-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .precedent-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .precedent-card:hover {
    border-color: #ffd700;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .precedent-name {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .precedent-quote {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .precedent-contribution {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* CALL TO ACTION */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .origin-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* RESPONSIVE */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .triad-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .precedent-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .timeline-connector {
      margin-left: 48px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .question-quote {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .insight-statement {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }

    .precedent-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline-connector {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
